<div class="page">
<section class="page-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="page-header a-fade-up">
      <div class="section-tag">How it works</div>
      <h2>Four steps. No dashboards to maintain, no accounts to link.</h2>
      <p>You hand us the raw material — renewal emails, invoices, PDFs, screenshots. We extract the details, form an opinion, and deliver it in a single email each week. No portal to log into, no app to install.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps a-fade-up steps-a">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-index">01</div>
        <h3>Forward or upload</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">Forward a renewal email to your perch. address, or drag a PDF, contract, or screenshot into the upload panel. Two seconds, done.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-index">02</div>
        <h3>AI extracts it</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">Provider, category, amount, renewal date, and cancellation notice period — pulled out automatically. No dropdowns, no tags, no manual entry.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-index">03</div>
        <h3>Get a verdict</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">Renew, cancel, or renegotiate — with the reasoning shown plainly. Not a vague nudge. A clear opinion you can act on or ignore in under a minute.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-index">04</div>
        <h3>Monday digest</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">One email, once a week: exactly what needs attention, ranked by deadline and cost. Nothing else from us in your inbox. No notifications, no spam.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

